                    "Q-MON-01.2: Does the organization utilize a Security Incident Event Manager (SIEM), or similar automated tool, to support near real-time analysis and incident escalation?.",
                    "Q-MON-01.1: Does the organization implement Intrusion Detection / Prevention Systems (IDS / IPS) technologies on critical systems, key network segments and network choke points?.",
                    "Q-MON-01: Does the organization facilitate the implementation of enterprise-wide monitoring controls?."
