                    "Q-TDA-09: Does the organization require system developers/integrators consult with cybersecurity and privacy personnel to:   -  Create and implement a Security Test and Evaluation (ST&E) plan;  -  Implement a verifiable flaw remediation process to correct weaknesses and deficiencies identified during the security testing and evaluation process; and  -  Document the results of the security testing/evaluation and flaw remediation processes?.",
